original: Collin, Tage Salomon, civilingenjör, Lidköping, f. 4/6/98 i Jönköp. av Johan C. O’. Gerda Holmberg. — Stud:-ex. i Jönköp. 16, utex. fr. CTH (M) 20. Anst. i ol. befattn. o. fabr. h. STAB 23-35, driftsing. v. Jönköp. & Vulcans Tändsticksfabr. A-B fabr. i Lidköp. sed. 35.
translated: Collin, Tage Salomon, civil engineer, Lidköping, b. June 4th, 1898 in Jönköping to Johan C. O’. Gerda Holmberg. - Graduated from Jönköping's gymnasium in '16, graduated from the Chalmers University of Technology with a degree in Mechanical Engineering in '20. Employed in the oil industry and managerial positions in factories at STAB from '23-'35, then as the chief engineer at Jönköping & Vulcan's match factory in Lidköping since '35.
